Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.26,0:00:18.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.85,0:00:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來自外部的攻擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,95區外壁 受創等級7
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:33.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法維持衛星內生存環境！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.67,0:00:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衛星的自轉控制系統怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.27,0:00:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布魯扎司令 請允許天神號（DEVA）出擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.26,0:00:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指停泊中的新型艦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.87,0:00:46.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有那艘船和高達
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.93,0:00:48.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以對UE發動反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.30,0:00:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 高達是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.03,0:00:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,監視系統緊急報告
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.22,0:00:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸造成衛星內各處異常震動
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去諾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.26,0:01:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不出6個小時就會扭曲瓦解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.86,0:01:01.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.17,0:01:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上安排逃生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣來不及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.37,0:01:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充其量搭載百人的逃生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知要花多久才能運完
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰艦天神號 準備啟航
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.96,0:01:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊急聯繫戴安·馮羅德艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.99,0:01:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是去反擊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.88,0:01:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了救出諾拉的居民們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.11,0:01:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用那艘戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那艘新造戰艦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.09,0:01:39.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始移居殖民衛星後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.63,0:01:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經歷數百年的宇宙時代
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.27,0:01:45.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爭奪地球圈霸權的戰爭偃旗息鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.19,0:01:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平的時代似乎降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和平卻如此脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.96,0:01:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現的未知敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.97,0:01:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令一顆殖民衛星化作宇宙的塵埃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這將成為百年漫長戰爭的開端
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.68,0:03:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們所在的諾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:55.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾拉核心部分的這段衛星主軸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與充當居住地的內壁完全分離
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.16,0:04:02.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此幾乎沒受到攻擊的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.49,0:04:06.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓居民們到那裏去避難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若用各區域的運輸升降機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:13.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疏散速度遠勝過逃生艇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:17.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 諾拉整體正在發生扭曲瓦解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.19,0:04:20.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以需要天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把天神號與軸心相連
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:24.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接牽引分離
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:30.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 軸心有獨立的維生系統
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:33.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 時間限制是5小時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.17,0:04:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不充裕但完全有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.91,0:04:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功與否全在大家的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.81,0:04:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.59,0:04:44.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對衛星主軸進行模擬計算
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:47.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 請讓我向天神號艦長戴安匯報情況
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將數據共享給天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 敵人會坐視我們的行動不管嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.31,0:05:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 希望也許就在那台高達
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.30,0:05:05.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保持秩序 保持秩序
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避難警報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.28,0:05:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家按照指示前往農業區升降機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重複
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家按照指示前往農業區升降機
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.14,0:05:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這貨是精密機械
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:25.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要輕抬輕放！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會有事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.20,0:05:32.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯 要把AGE構築系統運到哪裏去？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.29,0:05:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運到港口的聯邦船上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:38.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能晾在這兒被砸壞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.79,0:05:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE構築系統和高達合在一起才叫AGE系統
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:48.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達就由你開到船上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為防遇到戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.53,0:05:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶上光束槍和盾牌去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也會馬上去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要戰鬥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉 迪克也在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:10.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太帥了 菲利特真的在開機動戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉 為什麼來這裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去升降機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.63,0:06:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特不去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得把高達送上船
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道 菲利特也要一起上船？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:26.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.13,0:06:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 高達只有我能駕駛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是真的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 艾米莉快去避難吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:37.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是 你也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.36,0:06:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 菲利特！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快走會被留下的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:48.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 人家那麼擔心他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.28,0:06:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過菲利特說得對
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們趕緊去升降機
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:57.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉 你去哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:06:59.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船那邊 怎麼能丟下菲利特
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.96,0:07:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？怎麼都這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 諾拉也完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.81,0:07:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和當時一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:23.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人 沒來得及避難嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.64,0:07:32.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著 馬上來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.82,0:07:39.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼要逃？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.88,0:07:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再快點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.10,0:07:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏通向港口
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:07.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼打開？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:14.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裏怎麼會有孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是軍隊專用的升降路
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們想上港口的船
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.94,0:08:20.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.53,0:08:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平民快去農業區避難
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開閘門
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.41,0:08:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 果然被罵了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.73,0:08:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都到這裏了怎麼能回去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:44.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.07,0:08:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉 真是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布魯扎司令說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:09:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是瘋狂的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說要抽出衛星軸心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:05.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓天神號牽引住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.68,0:09:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打算怎麼辦 馮羅德艦長？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然不會聽他的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要沒有接到總司令部的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.48,0:09:15.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首要任務永遠是保護艦船安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.61,0:09:16.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.89,0:09:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓天神號立即撤離危在旦夕的諾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:22.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想對諾拉的人們見死不救？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.34,0:09:23.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還算是聯邦軍麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.36,0:09:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…古魯迪克副司令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.32,0:09:38.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您來得真早啊 戴安·馮羅德艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來傳達詳細作戰方案
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.83,0:09:44.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 你應該知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.51,0:09:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是聯邦軍總司令部的直轄部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:49.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要聽布魯扎的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道就讓開
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克 你…你小子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.58,0:10:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要提高功率 照樣可以要命
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘋了嗎 這是典型的叛國罪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:10.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪受罰天經地義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.48,0:10:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前提是 到時你我都還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.40,0:10:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.99,0:10:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.23,0:10:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是不是看到了不該看的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.47,0:10:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令 只剩下我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去天神號上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.89,0:10:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我要留在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.35,0:10:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分離衛星與軸心的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.14,0:10:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能在這裏完成
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:47.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法遠程操控
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.63,0:10:48.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道司令一開始就打算這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.77,0:10:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基地裏有司令官專用的逃生通道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:11:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專用的…逃生通道？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在天神號上協助大家避難
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.86,0:11:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拯救諾拉的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.77,0:11:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.78,0:11:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號托付給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.05,0:11:15.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,載著高達啟程吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.62,0:11:18.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…人類的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,專用的逃生通道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.87,0:11:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不存在的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我能說得那麼若有其事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.25,0:11:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 艾米莉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.49,0:11:53.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是聯邦軍的新造戰艦 天神號
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.23,0:11:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到實物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大好壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.86,0:12:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕放…輕放
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:09.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.40,0:12:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.93,0:12:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾米莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.34,0:12:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒去衛星軸心避難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來話長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們也上這艘船吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.00,0:12:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 艾米莉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別到處亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.35,0:12:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦橋成員去哪兒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.43,0:12:39.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴安艦長呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 查不到乘員資料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 現在是緊急事態
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.84,0:12:59.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠我們自己 讓天神號出港
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員 開始準備
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:10.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 軍隊的情報安保也不過如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.33,0:13:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號要為我所用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 別跑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.77,0:13:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這就下來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒受傷…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.77,0:13:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.19,0:13:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.75,0:13:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 那台高達是我造的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.47,0:13:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高…達？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.36,0:14:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:04.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高達一定會救我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.40,0:14:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願能趕上船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.19,0:14:34.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一時不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:39.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 別放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.59,0:14:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫菲利特 你呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:43.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.58,0:14:44.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚鈴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柚鈴怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.18,0:14:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,UE的攻擊好像還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亞當斯 你不覺得這次敵人的攻擊有古怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:13.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.49,0:15:15.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果敵人的目的是毀滅這座殖民地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:22.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,攻擊能源工廠就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:24.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.62,0:15:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古魯迪克副司令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.39,0:15:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是這艘船的艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.54,0:15:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.62,0:15:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才 聯邦軍總司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:40.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,BIGRing發來指令
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.32,0:15:44.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始 我就任這艘天神號的艦長一職
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.98,0:15:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操船成員與駕駛員登船了是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.65,0:15:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號 緊急啟航
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.63,0:15:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始連接衛星軸心的作業
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.20,0:15:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 高達還未搭載上船
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒時間了 讓高達自主逃離諾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.46,0:16:09.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天神號 出航準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.70,0:16:12.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令艦外作業的乘員返回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.18,0:16:15.44,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,660)\fs30}（天神號 出航準備完成）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.46,0:16:18.83,note1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,660)\fs30\fad(0,400)}（命令艦外作業的乘員返回）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:19.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼 高達還沒上船呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.36,0:16:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認遷留裝置分離
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維持周圍警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.28,0:16:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入出港階段一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.08,0:16:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.43,0:16:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來我們掉進最底層的隔離區了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.10,0:16:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在這樣 只能自己離開這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:16:59.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣直走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.35,0:17:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底右轉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你認識出口？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.21,0:17:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 聽我的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:14.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別忘記剩餘時間不多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.86,0:17:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員 開始連接衛星軸心的作業
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.13,0:17:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進方向上發現疑似機動戰士的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與襲擊諾拉的屬同類型
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.14,0:17:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時中止作業
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.96,0:17:30.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一級戰鬥配置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.73,0:17:37.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:41.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 被堵住了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 就這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,4 3 2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入宇宙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現高達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:11.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來成功逃出了諾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.14,0:18:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正與UE的機動戰士型進入戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 好不容易逃出來又和敵人撞個正著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.55,0:18:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能乾等著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是AGE系統派用場的時候！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.91,0:18:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AGE系統？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.20,0:18:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的光束武器不管用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.28,0:18:44.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼打？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.95,0:18:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲利特 聽得見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.59,0:18:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.67,0:18:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臨陣磨槍不快也光 使用AGE系統！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.70,0:18:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊 有AGE系統
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.59,0:18:55.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的解析數據呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.31,0:18:58.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數據的話 第一場戰鬥中收集到的足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:19:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上開始構築新武器
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:03.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.91,0:19:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 AGE系統到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.46,0:19:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是菲利特那小子造的好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.62,0:19:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運用生物進化原理製造的機動戰士構築系統
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會根據戰鬥經歷導出強化設計圖
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.96,0:19:26.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,系統會自己造出強大的武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.06,0:19:27.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:29.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 有了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.98,0:19:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入高速成形階段
